		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Really good comments here from the other players. And of course Scott your lesson is spot on. I would just add don&#8217;t volunteer for what you can&#8217;t fulfill. In my case I am getting offers to play with groups around town but I am still fully working my day job 40+ hours a week. To mislead them and say I can fill gigs and then back out will ruin my reputation and their gigs both.</p>
