		<description><![CDATA[I have found breathing exercises are a great help when facing stressful auditions. These are easily learnt - just focusing on the breath and slowing your breathing really helps focus your attention on that moment and not to fast forward your thoughts into the future where insecurity lurks sometimes. The other tip mentioned below of being in tune is also essential - check it right before you play the audition. Good luck.]]></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I have found breathing exercises are a great help when facing stressful auditions. These are easily learnt &#8211; just focusing on the breath and slowing your breathing really helps focus your attention on that moment and not to fast forward your thoughts into the future where insecurity lurks sometimes. The other tip mentioned below of being in tune is also essential &#8211; check it right before you play the audition. Good luck.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
