Hey, speaking of auditions, how does one get &quot;in-the-network&quot; of bass players who are available for big tours?  I mean, I see these (unknown to me) players backing some pretty big players for summer tours and get on dvd&#039;s and such; how does this happen?  Is it mostly word-of-mouth and friends of friends type of thing?]]></description>
