		<description><![CDATA[Good tips. I would add one. Make sure you are in tune. Have a tuner with you or be very comfortable tuning by ear. You may learn a tune in standard tuning and when you get to the audition, the band tunes a 1/2 step down. I have seen many people who can&#039;t tune or think close is good enough.]]></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Good tips. I would add one. Make sure you are in tune. Have a tuner with you or be very comfortable tuning by ear. You may learn a tune in standard tuning and when you get to the audition, the band tunes a 1/2 step down. I have seen many people who can&#8217;t tune or think close is good enough.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
